## Legislature of England, c. 1236 to 1707

This is about the Parliament that functioned from roughly 1236 until 1707. For any hypothetical new English parliament, look at [Devolved English parliament](/Devolved_English_parliament). For the one that exists now, that's the [Parliament of the United Kingdom](/Parliament_of_the_United_Kingdom). Don't confuse them.

